ze and annihilate groups in an instant.<br></li><li><strong>Co-op Gameplay:</strong> Team up via Steam Remote Play Together, combining efforts in real-time. <br></li><li><strong>Moon Eclipses:</strong> Experience dynamic transformations in the environment and enemies with each lunar cycle, encountering Sun, Ice, Fire, and Tempest moons.<br></li><li><strong>Empowering Transformation:</strong> Harness Madzik energy to evolve into a powerful version of your hero, gaining new strengths and abilities. <br></li><li><strong>Elaborate Boss Fight:</strong> Challenge the trickster Godkin, Fhum, in a complex multiphase battle that tests your strategy, skills, and endurance.<br></li><li><strong>Versatile Ability System:</strong> Engage with a flexible ability system that offers a variety of skills to customize your playstyle.</li></ul><br><strong>Play Madzik your way, with full Xbox/PlayStation controllers support, as well as keyword and mouse.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3023f6c4d10c66b6a62ec10cf9e75cf7.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3023f6c4d10c66b6a62ec10cf9e75cf7.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3023f6c4d10c66b6a62ec10cf9e75cf7.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/ece05fdeadc30c63649ebda91be906e7.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/ece05fdeadc30c63649ebda91be906e7.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/ece05fdeadc30c63649ebda91be906e7.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>For centuries, Zikverländ flourished under the watchful eye of Zik, the Sun God. However, the ambitious Turncoat Mage, Ahnglum, unleashed chaos by opening ancient portals, releasing alien moons and monstrous creatures. This brought the Nightfalls - a terrifying plague that causes madness and mutations during unpredictable eclipses.<br><br><strong>Heroes are now summoned to stop the Nightfalls, overthrow Ahnglum, and vanquish the demon God he serves.</strong> Embark on an epic quest to reclaim peace and sanity in the once serene Zikverländ. Champions, rise and put an end to the darkness!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3d47992fc329a849df9b2a3991c1e2c6.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3d47992fc329a849df9b2a3991c1e2c6.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3d47992fc329a849df9b2a3991c1e2c6.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/bf6c4c0074d0df4c6abdaf5c28d778c2.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/bf6c4c0074d0df4c6abdaf5c28d778c2.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/bf6c4c0074d0df4c6abdaf5c28d778c2.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/49a586bfaf7c2ac1b3cbecc0f952da7a.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/49a586bfaf7c2ac1b3cbecc0f952da7a.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/49a586bfaf7c2ac1b3cbecc0f952da7a.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Meet Makino, the Winged Bear: a furry powerhouse in melee combat, capable of charging into the heart of enemy ranks with his enchanted warhammer.</strong> Able to withstand lots of punishment, he can also bring the pain when needed. When Makino consumes Madzik energy, he reverts to his animal instincts, leaping at enemies to maul them with his razor-sharp claws.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/0a83478b149a502c901c8d87038fe0f9.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/0a83478b149a502c901c8d87038fe0f9.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/0a83478b149a502c901c8d87038fe0f9.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Deceptively adorable Veroline is a powerful spellcaster ready to devastate anyone in her way.</strong> She uses her magical abilities to control the battlefield and escape her attackers and when empowered by Madzik, she embraces her darker side and gains a whole new suite of abilities to strike fear into her enemy's hearts. <br><br>Switch between these mighty heroes and conquer any challenges thrown at you. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/badaf95a7b81c6c84e3766e2b9f9e36f.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/badaf95a7b81c6c84e3766e2b9f9e36f.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/badaf95a7b81c6c84e3766e2b9f9e36f.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/9f55df9218a2bda9965a955cedfb839d.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/9f55df9218a2bda9965a955cedfb839d.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/9f55df9218a2bda9965a955cedfb839d.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Set foot in lively handcrafted lands, filled with rewarding exploration opportunities. From wool to pencil, Zikverländ is shaped with IRL elements that bring a unique aspect to our game.<br><br><strong>Madzik is an unforgettable adventure, where moon madness, cooperative play, and immersive story-telling fuse into a one-of-a-kind retro experience.</strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>With the financial participation of the Canada Media Fund<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/a93be716c704c66283e1b3c9c70a6866.webp?t=1717681247\" width=150 height=58 /></span>",
